Hey There young traveler!
This is the secret Linux Escape Room cave!
This place is full of secrets and only the chosen can pass the cave!	
To get figure out how to get away you need to find the pass to the next room READMY filereadme file by following the clues and learning Linux:
Lets start:
This is what you need to do in the First room:
1. list the content of this folder in a sorted by size order and take the first letter of each filename and try to find the hidden message.
2. dont forget the hidden files too!
3. the pass to next stage is the hidden message in lowercase..
